body:
Thanks for your answer.

I did build Tensorflow from source and with TensorRT support, maybe I didn't specified the correct TensorRT location: I left the default location, I couldn't locate any TensorRT folder after installing it with the debian installation.

**EDIT:** I've also tried to install TensorRT with the Tar File installation but same error.
